sequenceDiagram
    Freelancer->>Client: Sends magic link (email)
    Client->>Portal: Clicks magic link (with token)
    Portal->>Portal: Validates token & Authenticates Client
    Portal-->>Client: Displays invoices and quotes

    alt Client accepts quote
        Client->>Portal: Clicks "Accept Quote"
        Portal->>Portal: Updates quote status to "Accepted"
        Portal-->>Client: Quote accepted confirmation
    else Client pays invoice
        Client->>Portal: Clicks "Pay Invoice"
        Portal->>Stripe: Initiates payment request (API)
        Stripe-->>Portal: Returns payment session/intent
        Portal->>Client: Redirects to Stripe for payment
        Client->>Stripe: Enters payment details & confirms
        Stripe-->>Portal: Sends payment confirmation (webhook)
        Portal->>Portal: Updates invoice status to "Paid"
        Portal-->>Client: Payment successful confirmation
    end